---
import { portraits } from "../data/images";
---

<section class="emma tint" id="emma">
  <div class="sec-label reveal">
    <span class="num">05 / Teacher</span>
    <h2>Meet <em>Emma</em>.<br>Your one teacher.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="emma-grid">
    <div class="emma-photo reveal">
      <div class="ph">
        <img src={portraits[0]} alt="Emma, Founder and Instructor at Studio 17" loading="lazy" />
        <span class="ph-label"><span class="sq"></span> Founder · Instructor</span>
        <span class="ph-tag">IMG · 05 · 3 : 4</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="emma-body reveal">
      <p class="emma-lede">
        Emma opened Studio 17 after a decade between London rehabilitation clinics
        and a classical studio in Manchester, with <em>one idea</em>: a reformer
        room where no one is ever left in the back row.
      </p>

      <div class="emma-cv">
        <dl>
          <div>
            <dt>Training</dt>
            <dd>Level 4 Reformer · Classical lineage (Polestar, Romana's)</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Specialisms</dt>
            <dd>Pre/post-natal · Post-injury rehab · Hypermobility</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Teaching</dt>
            <dd>Since 2014 · Every Studio 17 class, in person</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Off the reformer</dt>
            <dd>Runs, reads, quietly collects houseplants</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="emma-quote">
        <p>"I don't count reps at you. I watch, I adjust, and I remember
        where you were last week. That's the whole job."</p>
        <footer>Emma, founder</footer>
      </blockquote>

      <a href="/bookings" class="emma-cta">
        Book a class with Emma <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
